            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Bono Puero <lb n="2"/>P<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>osphoro</abbr></expan> <lb n="3"/>Laellia Cu<lb break="no" n="4"/>rillia pro sa<lb break="no" n="5"/>lute sua suo<lb break="no" n="6"/>rumque <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Altar oder Statuenbasis. Ursprünglich ohne Bekrönung und Basis gefunfen. IDR 3, 5: Z. 4/5: auch Cyrilla, Surilla oder Quirilla möglich.</p>
            </div>
